{"books":[{"id":"jfjb","name":"解放军报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"dates":[{"year":1969,"month":4,"day":4}],"page_start":5,"page_end":5,"description":"","is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"title":"高举毛泽东思想伟大红旗奋勇前进（朗诵诗）","authors":["五好战士王天瑞〖HH/换行〗DW：珍宝岛边防部队"],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"红彤彤的太阳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"普照海角天涯；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亮晶晶的雨露，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"滋润着亿万朵葵花。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"七亿神州，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飘扬的红旗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞舞的捷报，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"翻滚的钢水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喷香的稻花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都在欢庆我党隆重地召开了“九大”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“敬祝毛主席万寿无疆！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“毛主席万岁！万岁！万万岁！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欢呼声震天动地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"响遍了万户千家。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们前进在社会主义大道上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"更加斗志昂扬，意气风发。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"翻开革命的史册，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仰望真理的灯塔。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伟大、光荣、正确的中国共产党啊！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伟大导师毛主席亲手缔造，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"披荆斩棘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迈开英雄的步伐；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国革命的航船，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伟大领袖毛主席亲手掌舵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乘风破浪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迎来了胜利的朝霞；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国革命的红旗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伟大统帅毛主席亲手树起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迎风飞舞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红光闪闪普天下；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国革命的武装，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伟大舵手毛主席亲手创建，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冲锋陷阵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"横枪跃马打江山。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巍巍井冈山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刻印着毛主席豪迈的步伐；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"光辉遵义城，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沐浴着毛主席的雨露阳光；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"滔滔延河水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"映照着毛主席高大的身影；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天安门的红灯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"闪耀着毛泽东思想的光华。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忆往昔岁月峥嵘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看今朝烂漫山花。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"《炮打司令部》的春雷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唤起文化大革命的千军万马。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命群众铁拳奋起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对准大叛徒刘少奇猛烈冲杀；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖国大地怒火燃烧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把资产阶级司令部彻底烧垮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工人阶级必须领导一切，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命人民牢牢掌握印把。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向上层建筑领域进军，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"斗、批、改形势展新画。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"遥遥碧空千万里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红色氢弹腾空炸；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自力更生开新路，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"粉碎美帝、苏修核讹诈。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"虎踞龙盘今胜昔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长江大桥凌空架。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"列车满载红喜报，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞向北京迎朝霞。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看啊——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钢铁工人庆“九大”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天大困难踏脚下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抓革命，促生产，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喜报飞舞翻钢花。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看啊——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"贫下中农庆“九大”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抡镐劈山热汗洒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"摩天岭上种五谷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白云深处开稻花。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看啊——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命战士庆“九大”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乌亮钢枪肩上挎，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“三支”“两军”立新功，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖国江山似铁打。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看啊——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"知识青年庆“九大”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红色宝书手中拿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上山下乡把根扎，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千锤百炼开红花。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看啊——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“五·七”干校熔炉红，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命青春闪光华，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迎着朝阳唱凯歌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永远革命迈步伐。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"七亿双眼睛望北京，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"七亿张笑脸迎朝霞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"七亿颗红心向太阳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"七亿人民欢呼庆“九大”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伟大的党，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伟大的领袖毛主席，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命人民紧跟您，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千难万险脚下踏，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用毛泽东思想统帅一切，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"昂首阔步向前跨。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"望全球，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四海翻腾云水怒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"烽火燃遍亚非拉。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美帝、苏修日暮穷途，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命红旗遍地插。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乘着“九大”的强劲东风，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"前进，万众一心向前进；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高举毛泽东思想伟大红旗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"勇往直前奔向共产主义。"}],"alias":""},"tags":[{"name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"name":"北京文革","type":"人物"},{"name":"上山下乡","type":"主题/事件"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}